checkUnit

private void checkUnit(String _unit,
                       String _select,
                       String _target)
                throws matrix.util.MatrixException
Selects for dimension DIMENSION_NAME and _unit the _select and compares the result against _target. The check is done via Assert.

Parameters:
_unit - name of the unit for which information must be fetched
_select - select statement of the _unit for which information must be fetched
_target - estimated value of the fetched information
Throws:
matrix.util.MatrixException - if the values for the _select of the _unit could not fetched
